  <h1 class="index">Our Mission</h1>
  <img class="main-pic" src="images/front.png" width="284" height="73" align="right"  />
  <span class="topcontenta">Medical Arts is a family owned and operated business that has earned the coveted JCAHO certification. As a community pharmacy, we have been filling prescriptions for close to a century. We know the value of genuine service, and since 1979, have made our quality surgical equipment available to the five boroughs and beyond. 
  <p>At Medical Arts Chemists & Surgicals, our mission is to provide the New York area with one stop shopping for all your Home Medical Equipment & Surgical Supplies, as well as Pharmaceutical needs. Our knowledgeable staff combined with a large Home Health Care Product selection provides you with a unique professional and personal "neighbourhood store" experience.</p>
  </span>
  
  <hr />
  
